refsect1.para:
    On the ∼ command-line - which starts with a question mark
    '?' - the following commands can be entered:



	&par_n;



            Execute the action with number &par_n; from the list of actions
            that are possible in the current state. 





	&par_h;



	    Display a help message explaining the available commands.





	&par_q;
	&ctrl-d;



	    Quit ∼.
